unwavering spirit lives on

00:34:25.396 --> 00:34:28.065
in the thousands of people
and hundreds of Tribes for

00:34:28.065 --> 00:34:31.202
whom she fought and in all
those she taught to believe

00:34:31.202 --> 00:34:34.238
that it is never too late to
right the wrongs of the past

00:34:34.238 --> 00:34:35.640
and help shape
a better future.

00:34:35.640 --> 00:34:38.676
(applause)

