00:36:59.984 --> 00:37:02.353
demonstrate that
extraordinary skill that has

00:37:02.353 --> 00:37:04.655
made him one of America's
most revered and

00:37:04.655 --> 00:37:06.190
influential artists.

00:37:06.190 --> 00:37:08.326
(applause)

00:37:29.981 --> 00:37:31.315
Richard L. Garwin.

00:37:31.315 --> 00:37:33.985
(applause)

