that power technologies that
drive our modern world,

00:38:11.355 --> 00:38:13.524
Richard Garwin has
contributed not only to this

00:38:13.524 --> 00:38:15.860
Nation's security and
prosperity, but to the

00:38:15.860 --> 00:38:18.496
quality of life for people
all over the world.

00:38:18.496 --> 00:38:20.598
(applause)

00:38:41.519 --> 00:38:44.455
William H. Gates III and Melinda French Gates.

00:38:44.455 --> 00:38:46.390
(applause)

