00:39:18.322 --> 00:39:20.658
with their generosity
and innovation.

00:39:20.658 --> 00:39:22.993
Bill and Melinda Gates
continue to inspire us with

00:39:22.993 --> 00:39:25.963
their impatient optimism
that, together, we can

00:39:25.963 --> 00:39:27.631
remake the world
as it should be.

00:39:27.631 --> 00:39:30.568
(applause)

00:40:04.702 --> 00:40:06.303
