00:40:06.303 --> 00:40:08.873
(applause)

00:40:18.849 --> 00:40:20.851
Never limited by
conventional materials,

00:40:20.851 --> 00:40:24.088
styles, or processes, Frank
Gehry's bold and thoughtful

00:40:24.088 --> 00:40:26.490
structures demonstrate
architecture's power to

00:40:26.490 --> 00:40:29.794
induce wonder and
revitalize communities.

