A creative mind from an
early age, he began his

00:40:32.196 --> 00:40:34.965
career by building imaginary
homes and cities with scrap

00:40:34.965 --> 00:40:37.635
material from his
grandfather's hardware store.

00:40:37.635 --> 00:40:39.637
Since then, his work
continues to strike a

00:40:39.637 --> 00:40:41.639
balance between
experimentation and

00:40:41.639 --> 00:40:44.275
functionality, resulting in
some of the 20th century's

