00:40:58.689 --> 00:41:01.392
himself an exemplar scholar
of American innovation.

00:41:01.392 --> 00:41:03.360
(applause)

00:41:21.478 --> 00:41:22.580
Margaret Heafield Hamilton.

00:41:22.580 --> 00:41:25.015
(applause)

00:41:36.660 --> 00:41:39.563
A pioneer in technology,
Margaret Hamilton defined

00:41:39.563 --> 00:41:42.032
new forms of software
engineering and helped

00:41:42.032 --> 00:41:44.034
launch an industry that
would forever change

00:41:44.034 --> 00:41:45.169
human history.

00:41:45.169 --> 00:41:47.638
Her software architecture
led to giant leaps for

00:41:47.638 --> 00:41:50.774
humankind, writing the code
that helped America set foot

00:41:50.774 --> 00:41:52.343
on the moon.

00:41:52.343 --> 00:41:54.712
She broke barriers in
founding her own software

00:41:54.712 --> 00:41:57.681
businesses, revolutionizing
an industry and inspiring

00:41:57.681 --> 00:42:00.517
countless women to
participate in STEM fields.

00:42:00.517 --> 00:42:03.454
Her love of exploration and
innovation are the source

00:42:03.454 --> 00:42:06.557
code of the American spirit,
and her genius has inspired

00:42:06.557 --> 00:42:08.392
generations to
reach for the stars.

00:42:08.392 --> 00:42:10.527
(applause)

00:42:37.521 --> 00:42:38.656
Thomas J. Hanks.

00:42:38.656 --> 00:42:41.091
(applause)

00:42:50.301 --> 00:42:52.836
Throughout a distinguished
film career, Tom Hanks has

00:42:52.836 --> 00:42:56.140
