think big and to believe,
and inspired a new

00:43:18.762 --> 00:43:22.466
generation of young people
to reach for the sky.

00:43:22.466 --> 00:43:25.069
(laughter and applause)

00:43:49.960 --> 00:43:52.329
Deborah Murray, accepting on
behalf of her great aunt,

00:43:52.329 --> 00:43:53.664
Grace Murray Hopper.

00:43:53.664 --> 00:43:55.232
(applause)

00:44:02.773 --> 00:44:05.476
As a child who loved
disassembling alarm clocks,

00:44:05.476 --> 00:44:08.746
Rear Admiral Grace Murray
Hopper found her calling early.

00:44:08.746 --> 00:44:10.314
