(applause)

00:46:40.731 --> 00:46:43.267
Boldly challenging our
understanding of the world,

00:46:43.267 --> 00:46:45.636
Maya Lin's designs have
brought people of all walks

00:46:45.636 --> 00:46:47.971
of life together in
