00:48:06.583 --> 00:48:09.820
elements of our cultural,
political, and national life.

00:48:09.820 --> 00:48:12.422
Lorne Michaels' creative
legacy stretches into

00:48:12.422 --> 00:48:15.459
late-night television,
sitcoms, and the big screen,

00:48:15.459 --> 00:48:18.262
making us laugh, challenging
us to think, and raising the

00:48:18.262 --> 00:48:20.030
bar for those who follow.

00:48:20.030 --> 00:48:22.032
As one of his show's
signature characters would

00:48:22.032 --> 00:48:24.201
